author: Sophie Scott And Nick Sas
title: Virus 'here to stay' as experts outline Australia's coronavirus future
description: The experts behind some of the modelling used to determine Australia's coronavirus response say the country is in a "lucky" position, but warn the virus will remain part of everyday life.
content:
